data.description: Check out this show stopping stunner in highly sought after Sunset Hills Estates backing to the pond! Arguably the sweetest pad on the block offering 5 beds, formal dining, game room, & a theater room! Grand 2-story foyer, butler's pantry w/access to kitchen showcasing quartz countertops, designer finishes, & open floor-plan! Energy efficient, full gutters, 5-zone sprinkler system, 3-zone surround sound, & a pull through 3 car garage w/mud area & dog washing station! neighborhood pool & park!
